{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancelAll","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you add a task to a group after canceling the group,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that task is canceled immediately after being added to the group.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Immediately canceled child tasks should therefore cooperatively check for and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"react  to cancellation, e.g. by throwing an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CancellationError"},{"type":"text","text":" at their"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"earliest convenience, or otherwise handling the cancellation."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are no restrictions on where you can call this method."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Code inside a child task or even another task can cancel a group,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"however one should be very careful to not keep a reference to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group longer than the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"with...TaskGroup(...) { ... }"},{"type":"text","text":" method body is executing."}]},{"type":"aside","name":"See Also","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Task.isCancelled"}]}],"style":"note"},{"type":"aside","name":"See Also","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"code":"DiscardingTaskGroup.isCancelled","type":"codeVoice"}]}],"style":"note"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documenta